WEBVTT

00:55.680 --> 00:56.598
I think you're right.

00:56.681 --> 00:58.850
See? I told you.

01:26.836 --> 01:29.089
When did you get here?
You should have called me.

01:32.926 --> 01:34.052
Let me introduce you to him.

01:35.804 --> 01:37.097
This is my dad.

01:38.515 --> 01:40.016
This is the man I told you about.

01:42.352 --> 01:44.687
It's nice to meet you, sir. I'm Yu Ji-ho.

01:47.148 --> 01:48.191
I see.

01:51.402 --> 01:52.445
Let's go in.

01:55.031 --> 01:56.032
Open the door.

01:57.325 --> 01:58.326
Well...

02:00.620 --> 02:03.039
This was totally unexpected,
so you're probably uncomfortable.

02:03.832 --> 02:06.543
But I'd like the chance to formally
introduce myself some other time.

02:10.421 --> 02:12.966
- Dad.
- Come on. Open the door!

02:17.095 --> 02:18.138
Then I'll get going, sir.

02:25.770 --> 02:27.105
I said, open the door.

02:53.756 --> 02:54.924
Come and have a seat.

02:57.218 --> 02:58.636
I said, have a seat.

03:02.807 --> 03:03.975
Give me a moment.

03:04.434 --> 03:05.560
Hey.

03:08.229 --> 03:09.063
Jeong-in!

03:12.025 --> 03:13.443
For God's sake.

03:51.856 --> 03:52.899
Level One.

04:54.919 --> 04:56.921
Well, what does he do?

04:58.214 --> 05:01.259
He wants to formally introduce himself
to you, so ask him directly.

05:01.759 --> 05:02.844
When can you meet him?

05:02.927 --> 05:05.638
Stop being so reckless
and save yourself the humiliation.

05:05.722 --> 05:06.931
Just end it.

05:07.682 --> 05:08.850
What's there to end?

05:09.684 --> 05:11.185
We haven't even started yet.

05:11.269 --> 05:12.854
Is that why everyone already knows?

05:13.271 --> 05:16.024
How have you been behaving yourself?
Word has already spread.

05:16.107 --> 05:17.483
What do you mean?

05:18.109 --> 05:19.235
What have you heard?

05:20.528 --> 05:21.696
Am I married or what?

05:22.238 --> 05:23.990
It's not like I cheated on my husband.

05:24.741 --> 05:26.034
What have I done wrong?

05:26.617 --> 05:28.870
Who's talking about me behind my back?

05:30.455 --> 05:31.914
First, come and have a seat.

05:37.295 --> 05:39.047
What's with that attitude?

05:39.130 --> 05:40.882
Then what's with your attitude?

05:40.965 --> 05:42.425
Does being older give you power?

05:42.884 --> 05:45.470
Do you think young people
have no feelings or self-esteem?

05:46.471 --> 05:48.681
What if someone treated
your child that way?

05:48.765 --> 05:49.849
How would you feel?

05:50.558 --> 05:51.893
Stop talking such nonsense.

05:56.230 --> 05:58.066
That's how Mr. Kwon...

05:59.108 --> 06:00.651
treated me for four years.

06:10.661 --> 06:14.457
I hope you didn't take out the ones
that would upset me.

06:15.666 --> 06:16.751
No, sir.

06:17.293 --> 06:19.587
He hasn't really been meeting
anyone recently.

06:20.296 --> 06:21.964
Not even that girl, Jeong-in?

06:23.257 --> 06:24.258
No, sir.

06:27.595 --> 06:31.015
You can stop tailing Gi-seok,
but I'd like you to keep an eye on her.

06:32.350 --> 06:34.394
You know that she works
at the library, right?

06:35.603 --> 06:36.604
Yes, sir. I'm aware.

06:41.442 --> 06:42.819
It's the same every day.

06:42.944 --> 06:45.238
I go to work and come home.
That's pretty much it.

06:46.531 --> 06:47.490
What about you?

06:47.990 --> 06:49.742
Living in the US isn't any different.

06:49.826 --> 06:52.745
I go to work, come home,
and look after my kids. That's all I do.

06:54.247 --> 06:55.581
By the way, my wife called Father

06:55.665 --> 06:58.042
- and told him to visit us,
- Right.

06:58.126 --> 07:00.420
but he told her it'd have to be
after your wedding.

07:01.254 --> 07:02.797
So you finally got his permission?

07:06.676 --> 07:09.595
You should settle down and get married.
You've had enough fun.

07:13.099 --> 07:15.435
Hey, how did you get married?

07:15.935 --> 07:17.520
Father was against it, wasn't he?

07:19.313 --> 07:21.149
That was before Mom passed away,

07:21.232 --> 07:23.234
so I counted on Mom
and just fled to the US.

07:25.862 --> 07:26.904
I see.

07:27.363 --> 07:29.365
I should be there for you
and help you out.

07:30.491 --> 07:33.619
- I'm sorry I can't be a better brother.
- No, don't say that.

07:34.829 --> 07:36.831
Don't drag it out.
You should just marry her.

07:37.123 --> 07:39.083
What if some guy
snatches her away from you?

07:39.876 --> 07:41.419
Even if you're getting tired of her,

07:41.544 --> 07:44.922
other guys are bound
to find her attractive.

07:47.258 --> 07:48.217
You're right.

07:59.562 --> 08:01.814
- Where are you coming from?
- I was in the area.

08:03.191 --> 08:05.401
- Where's Eun-u?
- He's in bed.

08:06.319 --> 08:08.654
- Are you going to sleep here tonight?
- I'll see.

08:09.822 --> 08:10.948
Where's Dad?

08:11.199 --> 08:13.451
He's probably grabbing a drink somewhere.

08:14.785 --> 08:15.912
I'll be in Eun-u's room.

08:17.288 --> 08:18.456
Ji-ho.

08:18.539 --> 08:20.583
Mom, let's talk later.

08:29.008 --> 08:30.927
Anyway, it's stuff
you didn't need to know.

08:31.928 --> 08:33.221
I guess I shouldn't have said it.

08:35.723 --> 08:36.724
I'm sorry.

08:38.392 --> 08:40.186
I didn't mean to make you uncomfortable.

08:40.269 --> 08:42.146
Okay, fine.

08:42.980 --> 08:44.148
It's all cool.

08:46.108 --> 08:48.110
Then what do you plan to do
with Gi-seok now?

08:50.279 --> 08:51.489
I told you. We broke up.

08:52.198 --> 08:53.366
Who says you can do that?

08:55.076 --> 08:56.327
Has Gi-seok agreed?

08:57.370 --> 08:59.747
You unilaterally broke up with him.

08:59.872 --> 09:01.040
Dad.

09:01.123 --> 09:03.626
He still loves you.

09:04.335 --> 09:07.630
So I have to stay with him because of that
and act like I still love him too?

09:09.840 --> 09:11.050
Can't you do that?

09:13.636 --> 09:15.972
Can't you do that
and try to maintain the relationship?

09:17.056 --> 09:18.182
Dad.

09:18.266 --> 09:21.477
It's completely natural to get tired
of each other in a relationship,

09:21.561 --> 09:24.438
but making a conscious effort
to understand each other

09:24.522 --> 09:26.232
can help you bring the spark back.

09:26.691 --> 09:28.067
That's what I think.

09:28.651 --> 09:31.654
Besides, you two were together for years.

09:32.363 --> 09:34.782
How could you call it quits
and go cold turkey?

09:34.865 --> 09:36.367
That's so ruthless.

09:37.201 --> 09:40.454
And everyone, including your mom and me,
wanted you guys to get married.

09:41.455 --> 09:43.916
You can't let everyone down like this.

09:44.959 --> 09:47.712
Also, Mr. Kwon may have disapproved of you
before he met you,

09:47.795 --> 09:50.047
but he's very fond of you
now that he has met you.

09:50.464 --> 09:52.633
Hey, he's not perfect either.

09:53.134 --> 09:54.719
He can misjudge others.

09:57.638 --> 09:59.015
Dad, I'm your daughter.

09:59.724 --> 10:01.392
I told you he mistreated me.

10:02.268 --> 10:03.269
Jeong-in.

10:03.769 --> 10:05.521
Change your mind,

10:05.605 --> 10:08.441
even if it's just for my sake. Please?

10:11.360 --> 10:13.863
I can still work, you know.

10:15.990 --> 10:17.533
So this is about after your retirement?

10:17.908 --> 10:21.287
I'm embarrassed to admit it, but yes.
Help me out, please.

10:22.288 --> 10:23.706
I'll prove it to you.

10:24.498 --> 10:25.958
I'll show you what I can do.

10:37.386 --> 10:38.346
Did you tell Dad?

10:47.438 --> 10:48.564
Hi, Dad.

10:51.817 --> 10:53.402
I know you'll make a wise decision.

10:54.195 --> 10:55.363
I know you well enough.

10:59.200 --> 11:01.827
- Don't stay out late.
- I have something else to tell you...

11:03.371 --> 11:04.997
Why are you leaving already?

12:03.597 --> 12:05.516
Ji-ho. Hey, Ji-ho.

12:08.185 --> 12:10.646
Someone keeps calling you.

12:17.278 --> 12:18.320
Here.

12:38.424 --> 12:42.595
You didn't pick up, so I kept calling,
thinking you might be mad at me.

12:44.054 --> 12:45.639
Is your father still there?

12:46.849 --> 12:47.933
No, he left.

12:48.809 --> 12:50.227
Then why are you talking so quietly?

12:53.147 --> 12:54.190
Just because.

12:56.358 --> 12:58.778
- Where are you?
- In front of the building.

12:59.904 --> 13:01.238
The building?

13:02.615 --> 13:04.742
You mean my place?

13:08.996 --> 13:10.122
Yes.

13:11.540 --> 13:12.875
Why didn't you tell me?

13:15.127 --> 13:17.004
You said you were at your parents' place.

13:17.880 --> 13:20.174
What about Yeong-ju? Is she not home?

13:21.884 --> 13:23.344
It looks like she's asleep.

13:23.844 --> 13:25.679
It's okay. I called a taxi.

13:25.763 --> 13:26.680
Wait inside.

13:27.473 --> 13:28.974
The door code is 140719.

16:36.704 --> 16:38.706
Can I cook myself a bowl of ramen?

17:47.983 --> 17:48.984
Who is it?

17:51.487 --> 17:52.780
I said, who is it?

17:54.948 --> 17:56.366
I'm Lee Jeong-in's boyfriend.

17:57.367 --> 17:58.660
You came to the wrong place.

17:59.787 --> 18:01.830
I do have a lover, but not a boyfriend.

18:05.375 --> 18:07.127
You're upset again, aren't you?

18:08.170 --> 18:10.047
You're too easy.

18:27.106 --> 18:29.316
Go ahead and poke me.
I'm still going to do it.

18:29.399 --> 18:30.359
Do what?

18:38.450 --> 18:40.160
- You actually poked me.
- Sorry.

19:07.271 --> 19:08.605
I already saw everything.

19:35.299 --> 19:36.341
Thank you.

19:40.053 --> 19:41.263
Yeong-ju isn't asleep.

19:44.016 --> 19:45.142
I'm happy you're here.

19:49.354 --> 19:50.522
I have this book too.

19:51.231 --> 19:52.357
Did you buy this?

19:52.441 --> 19:56.236
No. Hye-jeong got one for me and Ye-seul
because she enjoyed it so much.

19:57.571 --> 19:59.489
There are many memorable lines
in this book.

20:01.283 --> 20:02.701
Well, let's see...

20:07.414 --> 20:09.249
Here, this part is nice too.

20:10.292 --> 20:11.877
Read it aloud in your lovely voice.

20:18.342 --> 20:19.509
"When we fall in love,

20:19.593 --> 20:22.471
must we get into it knowing
whether it will be fruitful or not?

20:23.597 --> 20:25.307
Can we approach love in that manner?

20:26.433 --> 20:27.643
We mustn't.

20:28.477 --> 20:30.354
We cannot be calculating in any aspect...

20:31.647 --> 20:34.816
because, after all, we love who we love.

20:37.319 --> 20:40.906
When one falls in love, it just happens.

20:41.698 --> 20:42.991
That's all there is to it.

20:43.700 --> 20:46.578
Hence, let's not wallow in despair,

20:47.037 --> 20:48.538
restrain our feelings,

20:49.081 --> 20:50.791
or smother the light.

20:51.792 --> 20:53.627
Instead, let's try to keep a clear head.

20:54.753 --> 20:57.464
- And--"
- "And simply say, 'Thank you, God.

20:58.215 --> 21:01.843
I'm in love.'"

21:18.944 --> 21:21.613
I didn't even have a chance
to tell him anything about you.

21:22.823 --> 21:23.991
Good.

21:24.366 --> 21:25.534
What's good?

21:26.368 --> 21:27.995
I mean, it's fine. Take your time.

21:29.871 --> 21:33.250
Are you saying that to be considerate,

21:33.333 --> 21:34.751
or is it because you're scared?

21:36.086 --> 21:39.131
I'm scared that you may end up
putting up with the stress all alone.

21:42.009 --> 21:43.343
I'm already losing confidence.

21:50.017 --> 21:53.478
I know I said I won't let you get hurt,

21:54.187 --> 21:55.230
but let me rephrase it.

21:59.318 --> 22:00.444
It'll be hard.

22:02.154 --> 22:03.947
You will be hurt,

22:05.657 --> 22:07.576
and you may end up hating me.

22:09.578 --> 22:10.579
And?

22:12.247 --> 22:14.708
I may end up becoming the person...

22:15.959 --> 22:17.502
who hurts you the most.

22:20.922 --> 22:23.175
Just don't use any of these
as an excuse later on.

22:24.676 --> 22:25.802
An excuse for what?

22:26.553 --> 22:28.722
Don't give me that as an excuse
for leaving me,

22:28.805 --> 22:30.766
saying that you're doing it for my sake.

22:34.478 --> 22:36.313
What? Was that your plan?

22:37.981 --> 22:39.191
Yes, it was.

22:41.985 --> 22:43.153
Don't storm off again.

22:46.031 --> 22:47.407
You know me too well.

22:52.537 --> 22:55.791
I think we're quite compatible.

22:57.542 --> 22:59.044
Is it because we're so different?

22:59.920 --> 23:01.380
Are you saying I'm ill-tempered?

23:02.172 --> 23:04.800
- I never said that.
- Whatever. It's too late.

23:06.510 --> 23:07.719
But don't you think...

23:08.637 --> 23:11.098
we'll be able to get through
everything together?

23:14.935 --> 23:16.061
Say yes, Ji-ho!

23:18.063 --> 23:19.064
Come on!

23:20.273 --> 23:21.358
Say yes!

23:23.568 --> 23:24.694
You won't say it?

23:27.864 --> 23:29.825
- Hey.
- Hello.

23:30.784 --> 23:32.035
What did you do at the weekend?

23:33.870 --> 23:36.873
Well, I did a bunch of things.

23:37.541 --> 23:41.378
"A bunch of things"? That sounds so free.

23:42.754 --> 23:44.131
You probably prefer working.

23:45.298 --> 23:47.050
Well, I can't really admit that.

23:48.218 --> 23:50.178
By the way, when are you getting married?

23:51.263 --> 23:53.473
Hey, Hyeon-su.
What did you do at the weekend?

23:53.557 --> 23:55.559
- Did you play basketball again?
- Well, obviously.

23:58.270 --> 23:59.312
Why didn't you tell me?

24:00.272 --> 24:04.568
Oh, I went on my own to get some practice.

24:04.651 --> 24:05.902
Not with the guys we play with.

24:06.736 --> 24:07.821
Let's go.

24:13.243 --> 24:14.995
Go ahead. I'll take the next one.

24:19.499 --> 24:20.625
Crap.

24:31.219 --> 24:32.596
Come to the meeting room.

24:57.120 --> 24:58.955
It looks like you already know.

25:02.375 --> 25:05.837
Don't jump to your own conclusions though.

25:07.964 --> 25:10.467
I don't want to ruin
my relationships with others

25:10.550 --> 25:12.636
just because of a personal issue.

25:14.429 --> 25:15.889
So don't walk on eggshells around me.

25:15.972 --> 25:18.099
Well, I was just worried about you--

25:18.183 --> 25:19.643
I'm sure you did it out of concern.

25:21.436 --> 25:22.687
But it actually offends me,

25:23.647 --> 25:24.773
so don't do it.

25:29.319 --> 25:31.947
And I'll never avoid running into Ji-ho.

25:34.991 --> 25:36.326
You must know what it means.

25:56.137 --> 25:57.931
This is driving me nuts.

25:58.515 --> 26:02.477
It'd be nice to have lunch together,
but I have a lunch meeting.

26:02.561 --> 26:05.855
That's okay. I'm just here to have
a quick talk with you about something.

26:08.483 --> 26:11.903
It's about my daughter, Jeong-in.

26:13.905 --> 26:17.117
Like I told you the other day,
it's not true at all.

26:17.617 --> 26:18.952
Is that what your daughter said?

26:20.537 --> 26:23.373
Who else, then?
I heard it from her, of course.

26:23.957 --> 26:25.333
So it's not true at all?

26:26.793 --> 26:30.797
Well, to be more precise, not exactly.

26:31.089 --> 26:33.383
What? You keep changing your word.

26:34.301 --> 26:35.552
No, let me explain.

26:36.052 --> 26:41.349
I'm sure her guy friends occasionally join
her college reunions and gatherings,

26:41.433 --> 26:44.227
where many people are gathered.

26:44.311 --> 26:47.772
It's possible that someone saw it
and got the wrong idea.

26:48.481 --> 26:51.568
You mentioned that you're suspecting it
"based on the circumstances."

26:51.860 --> 26:54.362
It was probably
due to something like that.

26:55.071 --> 26:57.532
That is my guess.

26:57.616 --> 26:59.701
So you're saying it's a groundless rumor.

27:00.368 --> 27:02.495
Okay. I'm sure the two of them
will figure it out.

27:02.871 --> 27:07.083
But do you think it's okay
to leave it completely up to them?

27:10.170 --> 27:13.173
I mean, misunderstandings like this
can happen again.

27:13.256 --> 27:17.218
And all the talks
can get exhausting for both families.

27:17.927 --> 27:20.430
If things drag out,
even the two of them might get sick of it.

27:21.681 --> 27:24.934
As they say,
"Strike while the iron is hot."

27:25.560 --> 27:27.687
I'd like to ask for your opinion.

27:28.271 --> 27:29.356
Well, you know.

27:30.607 --> 27:32.359
What are you thinking?

27:33.360 --> 27:36.071
Let's just nail down a date
for their wedding.

27:58.843 --> 28:00.929
I said you could take your time.
Have a seat.

28:02.597 --> 28:03.723
Come on, sit.

28:04.349 --> 28:05.642
No.

28:06.768 --> 28:08.853
- It's such a gorgeous day out.
- What?

28:17.278 --> 28:19.322
What's good about having a weekday off

28:19.406 --> 28:21.950
is that you can enjoy
a quiet afternoon like this.

28:27.414 --> 28:28.581
What are you thinking?

28:31.918 --> 28:34.796
I used to think this on my way back
to work from my lunch break.

28:36.047 --> 28:39.384
It'd be nice to chat and laugh
with the person I love

28:39.467 --> 28:42.387
while having lunch together in a park
on a beautiful day.

28:44.097 --> 28:45.682
Will that day ever come?

28:47.183 --> 28:49.269
It's nothing special,
but I've wanted to do it.

28:50.478 --> 28:51.646
So it was like...

28:52.355 --> 28:53.565
your little wish?

28:54.524 --> 28:56.359
There are things that I never got to do,

28:56.943 --> 28:58.695
even though they're nothing hard.

28:59.904 --> 29:00.989
For me,

29:02.115 --> 29:05.660
I've always wanted to walk along
an old alleyway

29:06.453 --> 29:08.913
after a heavy rain,
but I've never gotten around to it.

29:09.748 --> 29:12.709
It'd be nice to go
for a nice cup of coffee after the stroll.

29:12.792 --> 29:14.836
- Let's go together.
- If you behave yourself.

29:16.629 --> 29:18.715
Fine. I won't go, even if you ask me to.

29:18.798 --> 29:20.091
Sure. Try to resist.

29:20.508 --> 29:22.010
You're such a thug.

29:41.362 --> 29:43.490
It's a nice photo of you.
I'll send it to you.

29:57.504 --> 29:59.214
I guess you think you're very pretty.

30:01.841 --> 30:03.009
You are pretty.

30:09.933 --> 30:13.144
Don't say "no" or "it's okay."
You have to say "yes."

30:15.146 --> 30:16.815
- Let me hear it first.
- Just say yes.

30:17.524 --> 30:19.526
You really are a thug.
All right. What is it?

30:21.861 --> 30:22.862
Let's...

30:24.572 --> 30:26.241
go somewhere fun with Eun-u.

30:33.081 --> 30:34.541
I see that you're upset again.

30:35.458 --> 30:36.960
You're seriously too easy.

30:45.218 --> 30:48.012
I told you I won't date a guy
who loses his confidence easily.

31:08.700 --> 31:10.994
- You're already here.
- I just got here.

31:11.077 --> 31:12.078
Thanks.

31:13.913 --> 31:15.832
How much is the rent here?

31:16.666 --> 31:18.042
Why? Do you want to move out?

31:18.126 --> 31:20.378
No. My sister and I
might get kicked out soon.

31:22.630 --> 31:25.466
- Do your parents know about Ji-ho?
- They'll kick us out, right?

31:26.217 --> 31:29.178
How would I know?
I don't know what your parents are like.

31:31.598 --> 31:33.057
What are Ji-ho's parents like?

31:33.933 --> 31:34.976
Ji-ho's parents?

31:35.810 --> 31:37.270
Both of them are nice.

31:37.770 --> 31:39.772
They've been running a dry cleaner's
for a long time.

31:41.608 --> 31:42.483
What is it, Jae-in?

31:43.943 --> 31:45.904
It's nothing. Let's go.

31:57.749 --> 31:58.833
That night...

31:59.876 --> 32:01.502
I drank way too much.

32:05.506 --> 32:08.968
Do you think she's seeing someone else?

32:13.139 --> 32:16.643
If it's nothing serious, just let it go.

32:18.019 --> 32:20.355
You shouldn't nag her
about something like that.

32:20.438 --> 32:22.106
It makes you look petty.

32:25.151 --> 32:26.945
Her father wants to nail down a date.

32:28.905 --> 32:31.240
You two should discuss
and decide on the date.

32:34.702 --> 32:35.912
Okay.

32:44.879 --> 32:46.047
Why are you still here?

32:49.050 --> 32:50.093
Well...

32:51.177 --> 32:52.553
About your question earlier...

32:56.432 --> 32:58.017
Jeong-in is not seeing anyone else.

33:01.145 --> 33:03.147
She said the relationship with you failed.

33:07.193 --> 33:09.779
I was supportive
even after hearing that...

33:10.947 --> 33:13.408
because I was hoping you could
completely turn things around.

33:16.119 --> 33:17.370
Only admit failure...

33:18.204 --> 33:21.082
when you can call it quits
without any hesitation or regrets.

33:23.418 --> 33:26.337
Until then, no one really knows
who the winner is.

33:28.381 --> 33:29.841
Do you understand?

33:34.804 --> 33:35.930
There.

33:40.268 --> 33:41.519
Now you can set your passcode.

33:42.478 --> 33:43.438
Okay.

33:52.780 --> 33:54.073
Don't forget your passcode.

33:58.077 --> 34:00.163
It's all set now. Here, you should try it.

34:03.416 --> 34:04.959
- Press this first, right?
- Yes.

34:05.043 --> 34:06.836
ONLINE BANKING
FOR EVERY FINANCIAL MATTER

34:06.919 --> 34:07.920
ENTER YOUR PASSCODE

34:08.004 --> 34:09.088
Enter the passcode.

34:13.176 --> 34:14.969
- There.
- Yes, it's done now.

34:15.053 --> 34:16.304
BALANCE

34:17.972 --> 34:20.016
I can view the account details here.

34:21.392 --> 34:23.311
I don't have to go to the bank every time.

34:24.520 --> 34:25.980
When did you send me this money?

34:26.439 --> 34:27.899
Oh, it's for the booze.

34:29.692 --> 34:30.860
You didn't have to.

34:32.570 --> 34:34.614
Anyway, thanks. I'll put it to good use.

34:36.783 --> 34:40.203
Hey, give me a heads-up from now on.
I'll prepare snacks for us.

34:40.286 --> 34:41.537
Gosh, stop it.

34:44.040 --> 34:47.085
- I'll take them.
- What are you two chuckling about?

34:47.168 --> 34:49.045
- Nothing.
- What is it?

34:49.670 --> 34:51.089
- Dad, your phone is buzzing.
- What?

34:51.172 --> 34:52.924
- Lee Jeong-in is calling.
- Okay.

34:58.596 --> 35:00.056
- Where are you going?
- What?

35:00.139 --> 35:02.100
To check on the machine.

35:11.067 --> 35:13.152
SEONGDONG PUBLIC LIBRARY

35:22.036 --> 35:23.079
Ms. Lee!

35:24.455 --> 35:26.457
Hi, Eun-u. How have you been?

35:27.625 --> 35:30.711
Ms. Lee, you should come over
and hang out with us at our place.

35:31.170 --> 35:32.171
What?

35:32.839 --> 35:33.965
Oh, okay.

35:34.298 --> 35:36.467
- Don't say that.
- Why not?

35:38.302 --> 35:40.847
- What?
- Your daddy doesn't want me to come over.

35:42.640 --> 35:45.560
No, I was just kidding.
He thinks you're being serious.

35:49.272 --> 35:50.314
Ms. Lee.

35:51.190 --> 35:52.191
Yes?

35:52.525 --> 35:54.152
At the kindergarten,

35:55.236 --> 35:56.988
we made pinwheels.

35:58.072 --> 36:00.324
I made two.

36:01.075 --> 36:02.869
Oh, my. You made pinwheels?

36:05.538 --> 36:07.623
Why did you make two, Eun-u?

36:08.457 --> 36:10.126
One is for me,

36:10.710 --> 36:13.129
- and the other one is--
- It's for me, right?

36:13.212 --> 36:14.589
You made it for me, right?

36:15.006 --> 36:16.257
Yes, it's yours.

36:17.508 --> 36:19.218
Eun-u, you're a traitor.

36:19.302 --> 36:21.345
Eun-u, next time we meet,

36:21.429 --> 36:23.514
don't forget to bring the pinwheel
you made for me.

36:24.599 --> 36:25.725
Okay.

36:28.227 --> 36:30.563
Eun-u, do you want to meet my sister?

36:30.646 --> 36:31.647
Yes.

36:32.273 --> 36:33.858
Where is your sister?

36:33.941 --> 36:35.985
- Ta-da.
- Hi!

36:36.402 --> 36:38.112
You're so cute.

36:38.196 --> 36:41.490
Wow. Your sister is huge.

36:47.747 --> 36:48.748
Eun-u, gosh.

36:49.207 --> 36:50.416
You should sit back.

36:51.125 --> 36:52.335
Hi!

36:55.922 --> 36:59.091
A MOM'S VOICE 5 MINUTES A DAY

37:19.195 --> 37:20.196
Mom,

37:21.781 --> 37:23.199
I can do this.

37:24.367 --> 37:26.244
What makes you so confident?

37:28.329 --> 37:30.498
You said the reporters
will write about this.

37:30.581 --> 37:32.500
What if rumors
of your separation start spreading?

37:33.417 --> 37:36.254
It will anyway,
once the divorce process begins.

37:37.672 --> 37:39.048
Are you going to get one?

37:39.131 --> 37:40.591
What about the baby?

37:41.509 --> 37:43.970
I'll raise it myself
without his involvement.

37:44.053 --> 37:47.014
That's because you don't know better.

37:47.390 --> 37:50.893
Raising a child alone isn't easy.
It takes manual labor, not knowledge.

37:50.977 --> 37:52.645
Being smart won't help you one bit.

37:53.396 --> 37:55.815
I won't be able to raise the baby
as long as he's around.

37:55.898 --> 37:56.941
I won't be able to take it.

37:58.526 --> 37:59.527
Seo-in,

38:00.778 --> 38:04.573
you know very well that there are things
about Si-hoon I'm not happy about.

38:06.033 --> 38:08.661
Still, how things are happening for you...

38:09.370 --> 38:12.206
proves that you're meant to be with him.

38:12.832 --> 38:16.252
Marriage is a union of two strangers,
so of course personalities will clash.

38:16.335 --> 38:18.212
Spouses can be your worst enemy at times.

38:18.587 --> 38:21.424
But if you hold out
and endure the hardship,

38:21.507 --> 38:23.175
time will surely pass.

38:25.052 --> 38:28.639
Forget about everything else
and do what's best for the baby.

38:29.640 --> 38:32.977
Do what's right for the baby
and give Si-hoon another chance.

38:33.060 --> 38:34.228
If I do that, I'll die.

38:36.564 --> 38:39.984
I will if I have to be
in the same space with him.

38:42.028 --> 38:45.740
I understand that
you've fallen out of love, but...

38:46.949 --> 38:48.784
No, I'll really die.

38:51.329 --> 38:52.246
Seo-in...

38:53.539 --> 38:54.665
I need to live.

38:55.583 --> 38:58.085
I must live for the baby's sake.

39:01.839 --> 39:02.882
Is there something...

39:05.009 --> 39:06.969
you're not telling me?

40:00.856 --> 40:01.982
Since when?

40:05.277 --> 40:06.612
When did this begin?

40:09.156 --> 40:11.450
I'm sorry, Mom.

40:13.119 --> 40:14.203
I'm sorry.

40:14.912 --> 40:16.038
Nam Si-hoon...

40:17.498 --> 40:18.916
Where is this bastard?

40:19.458 --> 40:21.335
Mom, no. Please.

40:21.794 --> 40:23.254
- Let go.
- Mom.

40:27.091 --> 40:28.759
Why are you stopping me?

40:29.718 --> 40:31.846
You expect me to do nothing
after what he's done to you?

40:32.638 --> 40:33.722
You...

40:34.640 --> 40:35.891
You can stay put.

40:36.725 --> 40:39.478
I'm your mother.

40:40.438 --> 40:41.981
It's why I can't let this slide.

40:42.064 --> 40:43.732
Mom, please don't.

40:44.733 --> 40:46.068
I'll handle this,

40:46.444 --> 40:48.404
so just be by my side, all right?

40:56.412 --> 40:57.496
Mom...

40:58.330 --> 41:00.958
Mom, I'm sorry.

41:02.251 --> 41:03.669
I'm so sorry.

41:15.306 --> 41:17.683
Oh, dear.

41:18.350 --> 41:20.769
My poor baby.

41:20.853 --> 41:23.814
My poor sweet baby.

41:23.898 --> 41:25.316
That one, please.

41:35.701 --> 41:36.785
Yeong-ju.

41:36.869 --> 41:38.787
Hey, you're right on time.

41:38.871 --> 41:40.915
We have 30 minutes to talk.

41:41.457 --> 41:43.250
I thought about it,

41:44.502 --> 41:47.213
and I think I should've told my dad
when I bumped into him.

41:47.505 --> 41:49.757
If you had, you wouldn't
have been able to come to work.

41:49.840 --> 41:51.675
You would've been hospitalized.

41:52.384 --> 41:53.469
Then when do I tell him?

41:53.969 --> 41:57.223
Seo-in, Jae-in, and even you
are telling me not to.

41:58.557 --> 42:00.100
Can you really handle this?

42:01.310 --> 42:03.896
I know very well
that Ji-ho is a decent man,

42:03.979 --> 42:06.607
but being a single father...

42:09.401 --> 42:11.904
I can never make up my mind.
I really don't know.

42:20.579 --> 42:21.830
I do though.

42:25.000 --> 42:27.545
I think I know what will happen to me.

42:27.628 --> 42:32.716
Don't tell me you're already
thinking about marrying him.

42:33.842 --> 42:35.135
What kind of question is that?

42:36.345 --> 42:38.722
You'll automatically become a mom.

42:38.806 --> 42:40.474
Are you even taking this seriously?

43:04.456 --> 43:05.291
Yes, sir.

43:06.875 --> 43:08.586
No, it's fine. What is this about?

43:13.173 --> 43:14.675
Really? Oh, I'd love that.

43:16.135 --> 43:18.095
It's been a while since we met anyway.

43:22.808 --> 43:24.018
When would be best?

43:31.775 --> 43:33.110
- Jeong-in.
- Yes?

43:33.193 --> 43:35.613
- You've been getting texts.
- Oh, thanks.

43:49.668 --> 43:51.920
- Hey, Jeong-in.
- What do you mean?

43:52.588 --> 43:54.590
Gi-seok is meeting my dad?

43:55.257 --> 43:59.011
I'm not 100 percent sure,
but that's what Hyeon-su thinks.

44:00.054 --> 44:01.221
Unbelievable.

44:04.224 --> 44:06.060
I didn't know if I should call you,

44:06.894 --> 44:08.937
- but if they talk about me--
- I'm glad you did.

44:09.605 --> 44:12.274
Ji-ho, don't worry about this anymore.

44:12.816 --> 44:14.777
- I'll handle it.
- Until when?

44:16.362 --> 44:17.321
What?

44:18.739 --> 44:20.491
When do I have to hide behind you until?

44:33.629 --> 44:36.090
Ha-rin, who was that?

44:36.882 --> 44:39.635
I didn't see the name,
but whatever the text was, she...

44:42.638 --> 44:43.806
It seems serious, right?

44:45.933 --> 44:47.976
So it seems. What is it about this time?

44:59.321 --> 45:00.406
What's going on?

45:01.448 --> 45:03.158
My dad's meeting Gi-seok.

45:03.742 --> 45:05.536
Ji-ho's the one who told me.

45:06.453 --> 45:07.496
Is he angry?

45:08.205 --> 45:09.331
He's uncomfortable.

45:10.207 --> 45:13.085
All this time, he was patient
and suggested we take it slow.

45:14.545 --> 45:16.296
Why wouldn't he be annoyed?

45:17.339 --> 45:20.342
Even I agreed that you should
take your time, but I think...

45:21.051 --> 45:24.263
neither Gi-seok nor your father
will back down easily.

45:25.222 --> 45:26.849
So telling him is the right move.

45:26.932 --> 45:29.017
There is no right or wrong in this matter.

45:29.101 --> 45:30.602
It'll be painful for you,

45:31.812 --> 45:35.023
but I can't imagine the hardship
Ji-ho will have to face.

45:36.108 --> 45:38.694
I'll think of that when it gets to it.

45:39.862 --> 45:41.697
But that could be today.

45:42.364 --> 45:43.866
Gi-seok won't stay quiet.

45:46.452 --> 45:49.872
I don't care what you do.
Just stop it from happening today.

45:50.789 --> 45:51.832
Jeong-in?

45:52.833 --> 45:53.959
I'll let them be.

45:59.715 --> 46:01.383
- Yes, Ji-ho.
- Oh, boy.

46:02.426 --> 46:03.469
I wanted to apologize.

46:04.470 --> 46:06.638
I shouldn't have held you responsible
for this.

46:08.307 --> 46:10.058
Are you trying to make me feel guilty?

46:11.268 --> 46:13.145
I feel bad for making you worry like this.

46:13.937 --> 46:15.522
I think I should meet Gi-seok.

46:16.565 --> 46:17.608
No, don't.

46:18.692 --> 46:21.195
He'll only say things that'll hurt you.

46:22.905 --> 46:26.116
I'm worried that he'll tell your father
and make things worse for you.

46:28.118 --> 46:29.953
I actually want it out in the open.

46:30.120 --> 46:31.663
He'll know it sooner or later.

46:33.373 --> 46:34.500
I don't.

46:35.459 --> 46:36.502
What do you mean?

46:37.544 --> 46:40.506
It's about me,
so I want to be the one who says it.

46:43.050 --> 46:45.886
I'm not pressuring you
into introducing me to your parents.

46:47.054 --> 46:48.180
I'm just saying...

46:49.056 --> 46:51.225
that I'm not scared
to show people who I am.

46:52.142 --> 46:53.811
I like that confidence of yours.

46:54.645 --> 46:57.231
You know me.
I'm a sucker when it comes to your words.

46:58.607 --> 46:59.691
Well, I'm proud.

47:01.026 --> 47:02.444
I don't plan to let Gi-seok...

47:03.028 --> 47:04.780
have his way indefinitely.

47:06.406 --> 47:08.617
Being understanding and patient
isn't working.

47:09.785 --> 47:12.037
I'll meet him or call him--

47:12.120 --> 47:14.331
- It's not you.
- What?

47:16.333 --> 47:17.376
It's me.

47:19.253 --> 47:21.171
His goal is to take me down.

47:22.673 --> 47:24.007
He's not moving the clinic.

47:24.091 --> 47:26.677
How can he
when he can barely pay the rent?

47:26.760 --> 47:27.970
There's his wife.

47:28.387 --> 47:29.596
They're not on good terms.

47:33.600 --> 47:34.726
Is it your first time here?

47:35.853 --> 47:37.229
Is Dr. Nam here?

47:38.272 --> 47:39.523
May I ask who you are?

47:41.441 --> 47:42.568
I'm his mother-in-law.

47:43.443 --> 47:46.363
- Just a second, ma'am.
- I only need to know if he's inside.

47:46.446 --> 47:47.489
Thank you.

47:57.958 --> 47:59.960
DIRECTOR'S OFFICE

48:03.422 --> 48:04.631
Come in.

48:08.051 --> 48:10.804
Mother, this is a surprise.

48:10.888 --> 48:12.306
Are you in pain or something?

48:13.140 --> 48:14.349
I can take a look--

48:17.936 --> 48:18.979
Mother?

48:24.443 --> 48:26.862
Report me to the police.
Should I do it for you?

48:31.408 --> 48:34.161
Please hear me out first.

48:35.287 --> 48:36.580
If you lay even a finger...

48:37.372 --> 48:39.833
on my daughter ever again,

48:40.250 --> 48:41.418
I'll kill you.

48:46.381 --> 48:47.424
Are you smiling?

48:48.884 --> 48:50.510
Are you seriously smiling?

48:51.094 --> 48:53.430
How dare you smile!

48:54.514 --> 48:55.349
How dare you!

48:58.769 --> 49:00.479
How dare you...

49:11.531 --> 49:13.492
That's as far as I'll go today...

49:15.369 --> 49:19.498
because I'm too humiliated by the fact
that I let my daughter marry a bastard.

50:03.083 --> 50:05.627
Your delicious rice is ready.

53:25.744 --> 53:32.709
YOU'RE ALREADY A TREMENDOUS MOTHER,
FROM LEE SEO-IN'S MOM, SIN HYEONG-SEON

53:46.014 --> 53:47.933
And here are the dreaded children's books.

53:48.516 --> 53:51.186
I took a swift look,
and they're mostly damaged.

53:56.149 --> 53:58.443
Are kids this meticulous?

53:59.027 --> 54:00.570
They are by grown-ups.

54:01.279 --> 54:05.533
For this damaged books exhibition,
we should write a strong message.

54:05.617 --> 54:08.370
"The pain you inflicted
will someday be returned."

54:09.621 --> 54:10.956
It's the same with relationships.

54:11.998 --> 54:15.043
You don't realize that you've hurt
someone, but you regret it later.

54:15.585 --> 54:18.421
You can also regret it
without even realizing you were hurt.

54:19.965 --> 54:21.216
Who is more to blame?

54:21.967 --> 54:23.134
They're both guilty.

54:25.804 --> 54:27.973
I'm not saying
you're as bad as Gi-seok though.

54:29.557 --> 54:30.684
Thanks for clarifying that.

54:32.143 --> 54:34.896
I'm sorry, but I have other plans today.

54:35.772 --> 54:37.023
- What?
- Thanks in advance.

54:37.107 --> 54:38.233
What plans?

54:42.028 --> 54:42.946
Gosh.

54:46.783 --> 54:48.118
Jeong-in, where are you?

54:48.618 --> 54:49.869
Why are you asking me that?

54:50.745 --> 54:52.664
You've never asked me that before.

54:54.541 --> 54:56.042
To check if you're causing any trouble.

54:57.294 --> 54:58.420
Will you join me then?

54:59.379 --> 55:00.422
Of course.

55:01.673 --> 55:02.632
Ji-ho.

55:03.383 --> 55:04.342
Yes?

55:04.759 --> 55:06.886
I don't easily back down
from things I put my mind to,

55:07.762 --> 55:09.556
so don't worry.

55:09.639 --> 55:10.765
Where are you though?

55:11.599 --> 55:12.809
I'll come to you.

55:14.102 --> 55:14.936
No.

55:15.562 --> 55:16.813
You stay where you are.

55:17.355 --> 55:19.524
I'll be the one going to you.

55:22.193 --> 55:23.862
As long as I stay single, right?

55:25.113 --> 55:26.239
Date others if you want.

55:26.323 --> 55:28.742
I'll get in between you two
and take you for myself.

55:38.668 --> 55:39.919
Whatever happens,

55:40.378 --> 55:41.880
call me if you need me.

55:43.089 --> 55:45.008
I know that you're always an option.

55:45.717 --> 55:47.177
You never let me help though.

55:48.136 --> 55:50.055
That's how much I trust you.

55:51.639 --> 55:52.474
I'll call you.

55:53.224 --> 55:56.186
Are you going to where
your dad's meeting Gi-seok?

55:57.729 --> 55:58.855
I said I'll call you.

56:00.440 --> 56:01.274
All right.

56:01.941 --> 56:02.901
Be careful then.

56:03.860 --> 56:05.195
Sure thing. Bye.

56:21.211 --> 56:22.295
Let me.

56:24.255 --> 56:28.218
We talked about meeting up,
but it took us this long to finally do so.

56:29.552 --> 56:32.847
I should have called you first, Father.
I apologize.

56:33.348 --> 56:35.683
You're right. I was a bit upset, you know.

56:36.810 --> 56:37.852
Here.

56:44.526 --> 56:47.320
I thought about inviting your father, too,
but didn't.

56:49.531 --> 56:53.743
I also thought about inviting Jeong-in,
but didn't.

56:54.452 --> 56:57.872
It's fine. All we need
is a representative from each family.

56:57.956 --> 56:58.998
Right.

57:04.838 --> 57:08.383
I hear that Jeong-in's cheating on you.

57:18.768 --> 57:20.186
Why aren't you drinking any beer?

57:21.980 --> 57:23.189
I don't feel like it.

57:23.273 --> 57:25.191
Who drinks because they feel like it?

57:26.776 --> 57:29.487
Whether you drink or not,
I'm going to let you treat me good.

57:31.281 --> 57:33.074
Are you going to tell on me to my sister?

57:34.242 --> 57:35.785
I can distinguish my allies and enemies.

57:40.081 --> 57:41.416
But I'll be your enemy.

57:43.418 --> 57:44.794
It's only a joke.

57:46.296 --> 57:47.881
I'm not one to be loyal.

57:49.132 --> 57:50.884
I'll turn my back on you
if you don't do well.

57:52.135 --> 57:53.845
She'd do that and then some.

57:55.889 --> 57:58.433
You say that
like you've dated me for a long time.

58:02.103 --> 58:03.771
Give me a few pointers then.

58:07.650 --> 58:09.402
Is Gi-seok out of the picture now?

58:13.531 --> 58:15.325
If you're worried, don't be.

58:17.368 --> 58:18.369
What about my dad?

58:20.997 --> 58:22.207
I heard you met him.

58:23.541 --> 58:24.834
Did he even meet your eyes?

58:28.630 --> 58:30.006
Even though I'm his daughter,

58:30.089 --> 58:32.634
he treats me as if I'm invisible
ever since I messed up.

58:33.134 --> 58:34.052
That says a lot, right?

58:37.305 --> 58:38.973
I'm not trying to scare you.

58:40.183 --> 58:41.976
I'm telling you that he's difficult.

58:51.778 --> 58:53.863
Father, has Jeong-in...

58:55.365 --> 58:58.535
told you the whole story?

59:00.453 --> 59:01.496
Hold on.

59:02.121 --> 59:03.623
Is there something I should know?

59:04.666 --> 59:05.792
Is that the case?

59:07.794 --> 59:10.171
Well, it's just that...

59:10.880 --> 59:13.091
your father spoke about it first,

59:13.967 --> 59:16.594
so I thought you had said something.

59:18.054 --> 59:19.138
It's just...

59:22.809 --> 59:25.103
I think my father misunderstood me.

59:28.940 --> 59:30.149
A misunderstanding?

59:30.233 --> 59:31.234
Yes.

59:32.360 --> 59:37.323
You see, I got drunk recently
and rambled over the phone.

59:39.701 --> 59:43.246
I tried to correct him,
but he still got the wrong idea.

59:43.830 --> 59:46.874
He should've told me about that too then!

59:47.333 --> 59:48.668
Unbelievable.

59:49.711 --> 59:51.963
I didn't know about that,

59:52.547 --> 59:56.259
so I actually called you here
to apologize.

59:58.720 --> 01:00:00.680
You two have been dating for a while,

01:00:01.264 --> 01:00:04.934
so I understand
if you're in some sort of rut.

01:00:05.435 --> 01:00:08.438
But having another man in the picture?
That's just an absurd thing!

01:00:09.105 --> 01:00:11.524
Even on my way here,
I thought about it many times over

01:00:11.608 --> 01:00:13.192
because I knew it couldn't be true.

01:00:14.193 --> 01:00:16.571
I'm her parent after all.
How could I not know her?

01:00:17.864 --> 01:00:18.906
Of course.

01:00:21.409 --> 01:00:25.163
Then there's nothing more
to talk about, right?

01:00:25.246 --> 01:00:26.331
That's right.

01:00:26.414 --> 01:00:27.832
Good then.

01:00:29.709 --> 01:00:31.377
We just need to settle on a date.

01:00:35.173 --> 01:00:37.467
You guys haven't been moving forward.

01:00:38.051 --> 01:00:41.137
Mr. Kwon and I
had to get off our butts for you.

01:00:41.679 --> 01:00:44.682
I'm sorry. I promise to do better.

01:00:44.766 --> 01:00:47.810
Let's just get it over with
while we're on the subject.

01:00:50.438 --> 01:00:53.524
We should hear what Jeong-in wants first.

01:00:53.608 --> 01:00:55.526
What's there to talk about?

01:00:56.152 --> 01:00:58.905
It's already been decided.
All we need is a date.

01:00:59.656 --> 01:01:01.574
Just pick one that works for you.

01:01:04.035 --> 01:01:06.204
Has the food here always been this tasty?

01:01:08.790 --> 01:01:10.458
I think you should decide...

01:01:11.042 --> 01:01:13.461
on the date for us.

01:01:15.380 --> 01:01:19.425
Parents are better
at these sort of things, right?

01:01:21.260 --> 01:01:23.262
- I see.
- What do you think?

01:01:26.265 --> 01:01:27.392
You are...

01:01:28.393 --> 01:01:29.769
a lot like your father.

01:01:32.855 --> 01:01:34.023
You really are.

01:02:10.518 --> 01:02:11.686
I think it's her.

01:02:13.479 --> 01:02:14.522
All right.

01:03:20.630 --> 01:03:23.216
Gi-seok, don't you worry about a thing.

01:03:23.299 --> 01:03:25.134
I'll clear the path for you.

01:03:25.218 --> 01:03:27.720
This is where we first met.
Let's get married.

01:03:27.804 --> 01:03:29.263
I'm choosing this for your sake.

01:03:29.388 --> 01:03:32.475
Why did you even receive this?
You should've thrown it in his face.

01:03:32.558 --> 01:03:34.060
Gi-seok proposed to her.

01:03:34.143 --> 01:03:37.063
He must be bragging because it went well.

01:03:37.146 --> 01:03:39.148
Can we meet?
Don't tell me you're avoiding me.

01:03:39.232 --> 01:03:40.525
Sure, let's meet today.

01:03:40.608 --> 01:03:43.611
Hyeon-su, that blabbermouth,
probably told you what happened.

01:03:43.694 --> 01:03:46.364
How much harder
will you make it for Jeong-in?

01:03:46.447 --> 01:03:47.532
You're an obnoxious prick.

01:03:47.615 --> 01:03:49.283
You're doing this

01:03:49.367 --> 01:03:51.953
not because you want Jeong-in
but because you can't lose to me.

01:03:52.036 --> 01:03:54.163
- Just stop it already.
- I will when you do.

01:03:54.247 --> 01:03:56.541
I'm done being considerate to you.

01:03:56.624 --> 01:04:00.586
- Would you like to meet my parents?
- What if they're not fond of me?

01:04:00.670 --> 01:04:02.505
- Then we'll have to break up.
- Hey!

01:04:02.588 --> 01:04:06.008
- "Hey"?
- You know I didn't mean it like that.

01:04:08.511 --> 01:04:10.596
Subtitle translation by Liya Choi
